&lt;p&gt;Tab completion with the right prefixes makes it pretty quick to find what you’re looking for&lt;br&gt;if you already know something about the command:&lt;br&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;more&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
